    Base implementation of RDFHandler + AutoCloseable.

    The implementation of AutoCloseable allows for this class and its subclasses to be notified by RDFpro runtime when they are no more needed, so that allocated resources can be released if necessary. For this reason, it may be convenient to start from this class when implementing your specialized RDFHandler.
